SCIENTIFIC CALCULATOR SYNTAX

Natural Log (LN)
CORRECT SYNTAX:
LN(x)
INCORRECT SYNTAX:
LN x

Square (^2)
CORRECT SYNTAX:
x^2, (x+x)^2, x^(2)

Exponentiation (^)
CORRECT SYNTAX:
5^x, (5+2)^x, 5^(x)

Square Root (√)
CORRECT SYNTAX:
√(x)
INCORRECT SYNTAX:
√x

Cube root (∛)
CORRECT SYNTAX:
∛(x)
INCORRECT SYNTAX:
∛x

Special character e (e^)
CORRECT SYNTAX:
e^x, e^(x), e^(x+x)

Log base 10 (log())
CORRECT SYNTAX:
log(x)
INCORRECT SYNTAX:
log x

Trig functions (cos())
CORRECT SYNTAX:
cos(x), sin(x), tan(x)
INCORRECT SYNTAX:
cos x, sin x, tan x

Operators (+, -, *, /)
CORRECT SYNTAX:
x+x, (x)+(x), x*(x+x)
INCORRECT SYNTAX:
x(x+x)